>good 6x ClpXdN(62-424) + 5x(GGGGS)x8 covalent tether. Positive control by DESIGN (WT ClpX ATPase sequence, intact R307 trans coupler). NOTE: (GGGGS)x8 direct-fusion tether was gp16's 2-of-3-predictor FAILURE case (Boltz5/5 but OF3 2/5, AF3 1/5) - tether is a known confound, not a validated positive. Single-chain ClpX precedent: covalently-linked pseudohexamers (Martin/Baker/Sauer lineage; PMID citation not independently verified in-session).
